quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,94,"Ndipo Ife sitimatumiza Mtumwi ku mzinda wina uli wonse koma timagwetsa pa anthu ake umphawi, matenda ndi matsoka kuti akhoza kudzichepetsa"
  7,95,"Ndipo tidasanduliza matsoka kukhala mwayi mpaka pamene iwo adachuluka ndikukhala ndi chuma ndipo adayamba kunena kuti: “Makolo athu nawonso adali kuona zosangalatsa ndiponso mavuto.” Ndipo Ife tidawapatsa chilango mwadzidzidzi pamene iwo sadali kudziwa"
  7,96,"Ndipo anthu a m’Mizinda imeneyi akadakhulupirira ndi kuopa uchimo, tikadawatsegulira madalitso kuchokera kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi. Koma iwo adakana choonadi. Motero Ife tidawalanga chifukwa cha zimene adali kuchita"
  7,97,Kodi anthu a m’mizinda amaganiza kuti adali wotetezedwa ku chilango chathu ngati chikanadza kwa iwo nthawi ya usiku pamene iwo adali kugona
  7,98,Kapena anthu a m’Mizinda amaganiza kuti anali otetezedwa ku chilango chathu chimene chingadze kwa iwo masana pamene ali kusewera
  7,99,"Kodi iwo amaganiza kuti ndi otetezedwa ku chiweruzo cha Mulungu? Palibe amene angaganize kuti ndiotetezedwa kuchilango cha Mulungu, kupatula anthu otayika"